nyc_taxi = pd.read_csv(r'C:\Users\prita\OneDrive\Final Data.csv')

nyc_taxi.drop(nyc_taxi[nyc_taxi['Fare Amount']<=0].index, inplace = True)

nyc_taxi.drop(nyc_taxi[nyc_taxi['Total Amount']<=0].index, inplace = True)
nyc_taxi.drop(nyc_taxi[nyc_taxi['Trip Distance']<=0].index, inplace = True)
nyc_taxi['trip_duration'] = np.NaN

Calculating dependent variable:¶

In [4]:
for i in nyc_taxi.index:
    nyc_taxi['trip_duration'][i] = (datetime.strptime(nyc_taxi['Lpep Dropoff Datetime'][i],'%d-%m-%Y %H:%M:%S') - datetime.strptime(nyc_taxi['Lpep Pickup Datetime'][i], '%d-%m-%Y %H:%M:%S')).total_seconds()
nyc_taxi.drop(nyc_taxi[nyc_taxi['trip_duration']<0].index, inplace = True)

Outliers removal:¶

In [5]:
nyc_taxi['z_score'] = zscore(nyc_taxi['trip_duration'])
nyc_taxi.drop(nyc_taxi[(nyc_taxi['z_score']>3.0)|(nyc_taxi['z_score']< -3.0)].index, inplace = True)
nyc_taxi.head(10)
nyc_taxi.drop(['z_score'], axis = 1, inplace = True)

Standardisation:¶

In [18]:
def standardisation(data):
    return ((data-data.mean())/data.std())

def var_inf_factor(data):
    vif = pd.DataFrame()
    vif['Feature'] = data.columns
    vif['Factor'] = [variance_inflation_factor(data.values, i) for i in range(data.shape[1])]
    print(vif)

def residual_plot(model):
    plt.scatter(standardisation(model.fittedvalues), standardisation(model.resid));
    plt.title('Residual Plot');
    plt.xlabel('Standardised Predicted Values');
    plt.ylabel('Standardised Residue Values');

def cooks_plot(model):
